    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246600/extras/1acc7688c4477df0c5391488038808d6.poster.avif?t=1761183156\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246600/extras/1acc7688c4477df0c5391488038808d6.webm?t=1761183156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246600/extras/1acc7688c4477df0c5391488038808d6.mp4?t=1761183156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你正要执行你的第一个任务，但是出了可怕的错。现在，你被困在一个与世隔绝的科研综合体内，研究人员已经失踪，而你本应监督的人工智能已经失控。你和周围人的命运取决于你的言行和决定。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你将会遇到：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第一人称心理恐怖游戏，包含探索和解谜元素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246600/extras/8850c75e76491a1b0c0cc10b0f119b28.poster.avif?t=1761183156\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246600/extras/8850c75e76491a1b0c0cc10b0f119b28.webm?t=1761183156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246600/extras/8850c75e76491a1b0c0cc10b0f119b28.mp4?t=1761183156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由先进AI驱动的NPC，能够实时对你的选择做出反应。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246600/extras/7b2804c8889d1455967a843a8e1d9cdb.poster.avif?t=1761183156\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246600/extras/7b2804c8889d1455967a843a8e1d9cdb.webm?t=1